Soul Fusion: Special Edition is jam-packed with value! Not only does it include 3 booster packs of Soul Fusion, each box is guaranteed 1 of 2 Super Rare variant cards, as well as 1 of 2 Super Rare preview cards of non-foil cards from the upcoming Winter 2019 booster set!

Each display comes with 10 Soul Fusion: Special Edition Boxes.
